Hey all, just a reminder that @sudeep’s Tech Talk, “Observability Deep Dive_”_ is starting in a few minutes at 8:15am PT am. It will be great opportunity to learn about how we can use stats and metrics at Instabase.
*When*: Thursday 09/02 8:15-9:00am PT
*Where*: https://instabase.zoom.us/j/99786303892
*More info and recordings*: Tech talk confluence page (https://instabase.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/IB/pages/1263468737/IB+Tech+Talks)
Help us all read Grafana boards :slightly_smiling_face:

Hi everyone, thanks for joining in on the Obsevability deepdive today! If you have any questions or thoughts, please send them our way at <#C01DJ7QDC2H|> !

Here are the slides from the talk today - presentation link (https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/17GNmKEYTJgIpvfy4f7Q91z8jYt4SN7qUS3ZIX3b6LQY/edit?usp=sharing)

We also have documentation for stats available for use now! Links in the slide and also copied here for reference -
Observability and Stats - Overview (https://docs.google.com/document/d/1xLRCTbsylckEXRfhc0coUTUT-PA3PsAaZbCnWnNQUNY/edit#)
